{"tid":2124121,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共戰機深夜闖空域 台派多架軍機驅趕","createTime":"2020-07-25T07:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T07:23:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a89d02e211fd36547d2559f078ee807dd5efddca","tid":2124121,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:22:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200725/DGO2F5NNNSDQW5MEA65N5ZRAXM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200725%2FDGO2F5NNNSDQW5MEA65N5ZRAXM%2F&d=jSYRdVihxMCX8m9Ry8wFHQjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=e0a124bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200725%2FDGO2F5NNNSDQW5MEA65N5ZRAXM%2F&h=92557f3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200725/DGO2F5NNNSDQW5MEA65N5ZRAXM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中共戰機深夜闖空域 台派多架軍機驅趕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Swwn2HHzSbm-xcL4McxxznhOFSc=/190x121/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KVUOQYUC6ON3UNILUGKZVB7TWQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSwwn2HHzSbm-xcL4McxxznhOFSc%3D%2F190x121%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKVUOQYUC6ON3UNILUGKZVB7TWQ.gif&h=78d27502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nF-16戰機深夜升空攔截解放軍戰機。<br />\n<br />\n大陸近月在台海空域軍事動作頻頻，解放軍戰機前日罕見地在晚上闖入台灣的西南空域，台灣空軍派出戰機緊急升空攔截驅離。據指，花蓮、台南、嘉義及台中的空軍基地，接連出動戰機應對，兩岸空域緊張情勢一觸即發。<br />\n<br />\n前日深夜開始，台灣各地都有民眾目擊戰機深夜緊急升空，台媒援引當地軍事迷提供的消息稱，前晚至昨日凌晨期間，中共軍機多次「侵犯台灣西南空域」，台灣空軍包括嘉義丶台南丶花蓮在內的多個空軍基地，出動F-16丶IDF戰機連番緊急升空及監控，並對中共軍機警告驅離。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美反潛巡邏機南海偵察<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：參院通過《國防授權法》 倡「六項保證」  美部署邀台參加環太軍演<br />\n<br />\n根據台軍紀錄，解放軍軍機曾在今年3月16日晚間，在台灣西南方外圍空域首度進行夜航訓練。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"0e1c24adcb509385ee8fa644ae9702c5c009f3ed","tid":2124121,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T07:23:46.000Z","msg":"番去救災啦on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}